304
00:27:23,480 --> 00:27:25,000
Don't play dumb.

305
00:27:25,240 --> 00:27:28,720
You told her that you drank that mixture she gave you.

306
00:27:29,240 --> 00:27:32,000
You know perfectly well that isn't true.

307
00:27:32,480 --> 00:27:34,240
