311
00:27:43,720 --> 00:27:45,000
So what?

312
00:27:45,493 --> 00:27:47,480
Now you've discovered Nueng has Royal blood,

313
00:27:47,480 --> 00:27:48,480
You take her side?

314
00:27:48,480 --> 00:27:49,480
Piengfah!

315
