So tell me this.

316
00:27:52,256 --> 00:27:55,480
Why did you have to hit Anueng with a cane?

317
00:27:59,240 --> 00:28:00,720
How could you do that?

318
00:28:01,720 --> 00:28:03,000
She's your granddaughter.

319
00:28:03,000 --> 00:28:05,480
