It'd be strange if I didn't know.

342
00:30:07,480 --> 00:30:09,720
That's why Piengfah chose next Saturday.

343
00:30:10,720 --> 00:30:12,480
You've done your research I see.

344
00:30:15,720 --> 00:30:19,000
It's my daughter's birthday. Please let me come.

345
00:30:21,010 --> 00:30:22,480
Please let me join as well.

346
00:30:25,720 --> 00:30:27,000
You've been eavesdropping on us?

347
00:30:29,480 --> 00:30:30,720
Who is this?

348
00:30:31,516 --> 00:30:34,000
A guy with a crush on your daughter.

349
00:30:35,720 --> 00:30:39,000
Hey. Have you stopped stalking Anueng?

350
00:30:40,480 --> 00:30:44,000
Yes. I stopped as soon as you spoke to me.

351
00:30:44,720 --> 00:30:46,480
I'm sorry.

352
00:30:48,240 --> 00:30:49,720
He stalked Anueng?

353
00:30:51,000 --> 00:30:54,720
This guy stalked my daughter like a psycho?

354
