364
00:31:45,000 --> 00:31:46,000
Anueng.

365
00:31:47,720 --> 00:31:50,480
Everyone is her for you today.

366
00:31:54,240 --> 00:31:55,240
Yes.

367
00:32:00,000 --> 00:32:02,480
