372
00:32:21,240 --> 00:32:23,000
You have a father.

373
00:32:26,240 --> 00:32:27,240
Nueng.

374
00:32:28,000 --> 00:32:31,000
You should have given her more time.

375
00:32:33,480 --> 00:32:34,720
And Folk.

376
00:32:39,240 --> 00:32:41,000
He has a crush on you.

377
00:32:57,000 --> 00:32:59,480
Ah … Miss Nueng. I'm scared.

378
00:33:00,480 --> 00:33:03,000
Hey. Stop pretending.

379
00:33:03,480 --> 00:33:06,480
I was practicing. Can't I practice being scared?

380
00:33:09,480 --> 00:33:12,240
Well … I have to go to the toilet.

381
00:33:12,240 --> 00:33:14,480
Wait Miss Anueng. I'll go with you.

382
00:33:15,480 --> 00:33:17,000
It's your turn now.

383
00:33:30,480 --> 00:33:31,480
Ahhh!

384
00:35:00,000 --> 00:35:01,000
Are you having fun?

385
00:35:01,000 --> 00:35:03,000
There's an ice cream stall. Do you want some?

386
00:35:06,240 --> 00:35:08,720
Do you want popcorn. There's some there.

387
00:35:28,720 --> 00:35:30,720
Anueng hasn't spoken to me once.

388
00:35:31,720 --> 00:35:33,000
Me either.

389
00:35:35,240 --> 00:35:38,000
I wanted to spend some quality time with my daughter.

390
00:35:38,000 --> 00:35:40,000
Why did you invite strangers?

391
00:35:40,500 --> 00:35:42,000
Is Chet a stranger?

392
00:35:43,720 --> 00:35:46,720
Well, you shouldn't have invited that boy.

393
00:35:46,720 --> 00:35:48,000
Look at them.

394
00:35:48,000 --> 00:35:50,480
I haven't had a chance to spend any time with my daughter.

395
00:35:51,504 --> 00:35:53,000
If that boy wasn't here,

396
00:35:54,240 --> 00:35:56,000
