400
00:36:05,720 --> 00:36:07,720
None of your business.

401
00:36:09,480 --> 00:36:11,480
You need to give Anueng time.

402
00:36:41,720 --> 00:36:45,480
You don't want me to take Anueng to America right?

403
00:36:47,480 --> 00:36:49,000
What do you mean?

404
00:36:50,480 --> 00:36:53,240
Anueng sees you as a hero,

405
00:36:53,240 --> 00:36:55,240
