413
00:37:14,000 --> 00:37:15,480
Satisfied now?

414
00:37:16,276 --> 00:37:19,240
I'll be satisfied … when you do it. 

415
00:37:20,000 --> 00:37:22,000
What are you waiting for?

416
00:37:39,000 --> 00:37:40,000
Anueng.

417
00:37:42,720 --> 00:37:45,000
I need to talk to you about something.

418
00:37:53,720 --> 00:37:55,000
What's wrong?

419
00:37:57,720 --> 00:37:59,240
Nothing.

420
00:38:02,000 --> 00:38:04,000
I'm asking what's wrong?

421
00:38:10,000 --> 00:38:13,480
I haven't said anything yet. Why are you crying?

422
00:38:16,249 --> 00:38:19,481
I'm not crying because of what you might say.

423
00:38:20,240 --> 00:38:22,240
I'm just sad.

424
00:38:24,240 --> 00:38:26,000
Why are you sad?

425
00:38:27,240 --> 00:38:30,000
You want me to go and live with my mother in America.

426
00:38:33,480 --> 00:38:35,000
How do you know?

427
00:38:37,240 --> 00:38:39,479
I overheard my mother and grandma talking.

428
00:38:42,480 --> 00:38:45,240
I don't know what I'm most sad about.

429
00:38:47,720 --> 00:38:51,720
You lying to me and trying to make me go with my mother.

430
00:38:54,720 --> 00:38:56,240
Or Mr Chet,

431
00:38:57,480 --> 00:38:59,240
The guy who was flirting with you,

432
00:39:01,720 --> 00:39:04,000
Suddenly becomes my father.

433
00:39:07,720 --> 00:39:09,240
Or that guy.

434
00:39:10,783 --> 00:39:12,783
Why did you invite him today?

435
00:39:13,720 --> 00:39:16,480
I'm not interested in him.

436
00:39:20,240 --> 00:39:22,240
I think what I'm most sad about,

437
00:39:26,720 --> 00:39:28,480
Is you.

438
00:39:34,720 --> 00:39:36,720
I just want the best for you.

439
00:39:38,240 --> 00:39:40,000
I invited Folk,

440
00:39:43,240 --> 00:39:45,240
So you wouldn't be bored.

441
00:39:46,720 --> 00:39:48,240
As for your parents,

442
00:39:51,000 --> 00:39:52,480
