454
00:40:51,000 --> 00:40:52,480
Whether I have feelings or not.

455
00:40:53,000 --> 00:40:54,720
You can think what you want.

456
00:40:55,240 --> 00:40:57,000
It's up to you.

457
00:41:00,720 --> 00:41:02,720
